roposed user\nbarring algorithm is applied, simulations demonstrate that the instantaneous\nthroughput of NOMA-RA always remains close to the maximum throughput confirming\nthe effectiveness of our load regulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Feb 2020 21:57:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
