tem is practical, with a low-complexity\nreal-time encoder and a cascade decoder consisting of a fast initial decoder\nand an optional CNN soft decoder.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 00:33:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
