le ductility of\nthe GS material. The model allows to investigate the mechanical response and\noptimize the properties of materials with various types of spatially\nheterogeneous grain microstructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 14:21:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
